      "description": "This car is in fair condition. The exterior has several scratches, minor dents, and some surface rust in a few areas. The interior shows considerable wear \u2014 the upholstery is faded and worn in high-contact areas, and some trim pieces show age. Mechanically the car runs, but it will likely need some attention in the near term.",
